title: Photos: Sunnyvale QB Caleb McDill throws for 359 yards, 5 TDs as they defeat Life Oak Cliff, 66-28
text: Sunnyvale quarterback Caleb McDill (12) steps up into the pocket and fires a touchdown pass to Raiders receiver Cash Goodhart (5) during second quarter action against Life Oak Cliff. The two teams played their football game at Longhorn Stadium in Cedar Hill on October16, 2015. (Steve Hamm/Special Contributor)
